title: Warwick 26/5/16
body: So i was playing a match, was doing exceptionally well with warwick, and got my whole team fed, when i finished the match expecting to get an s+ or atleast an s-, but i only got an A+, SERIOUSLY WHAT KDA DO U NEED TO GET AN S+ 100/0??!!!, This is bs

replies.body:
